species.name: toucannon
descriptions: Known for forming harmonious couples, this Pokémon is brought to wedding ceremonies as a good luck charm.
They smack beaks with others of their kind to communicate. The strength and number of hits tell each other how they feel.
When it battles, its beak heats up. The temperature can easily exceed 212 degrees Fahrenheit, causing severe burns when it hits.
Within its beak, its internal gas ignites, explosively launching seeds with enough power to pulverize boulders.

abilities.name: skill-link
abilities.effect: Extends two-to-five-hit moves and triple kick to their full length every time.

abilities.name: sheer-force
abilities.effect: Strengthens moves with extra effects to 1.3× their power, but prevents their extra effects.
